The only thing need to be done before building and running this service is:

1- Change the fileName in ScrabbleService class to reflect where is dictionary files are.

One fileName is provided then:

for mac and linux users :
1- extract the file
2- open terminal and cd to the directory then run

	./gradlew build tomcatRunWar

once the build finish successfully, then open a browser/POstman and run: http://localhost:8080/words/tah (change tah to any word you want to test)

for windows users :
1- extract the file
2- open cmd and cd to the directory then run

	gradlew build tomcatRunWar

once the build finish successfully, then open a browser/POstman and run: http://localhost:8080/words/tah (change tah to any word you want to test)
